# Image Directory

Place your images in the following subdirectories:

## Blog Images
`/images/blog/` - Images for blog posts

## Project Images
`/images/projects/` - Images for projects

## General
`/images/` - Other images (avatar, etc.)

## Recommended Image Sizes

- Blog post featured images: 1200x630px
- Project screenshots: 1920x1080px or 16:9 ratio
- Avatar/Profile: 400x400px (square)

## Supported Formats

- JPEG (.jpg, .jpeg)
- PNG (.png)
- WebP (.webp)
- AVIF (.avif)

## Optimization Tips

1. Compress images before adding them
2. Use WebP format for better performance
3. Use descriptive file names (e.g., `next-js-tutorial.jpg`)
4. Avoid spaces in file names (use hyphens instead)

## Tools for Image Optimization

- [TinyPNG](https://tinypng.com/)
- [Squoosh](https://squoosh.app/)
- [ImageOptim](https://imageoptim.com/) (Mac)
